Titolo: SanctuaryRPG

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: SanctuaryRPG is a roguelike adventure video game developed by Black Shell Games, a subsidiary of Black Shell Media LLC. The game was released on April 29, 2014 for Microsoft Windows. In the game, players create a character and travel throughout the game vanquishing enemies, crafting items, and collecting loot, with the ultimate goal of defeating The Matron.